{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "739d2fc1-d05b-4936-b531-146473fb913c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/739d2fc1-d05b-4936-b531-146473fb913c@1.pkg/1772597635065/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597635760", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/739d2fc1-d05b-4936-b531-146473fb913c@1.pkg/1772597635065/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597635760"}, "identifier": "739d2fc1-d05b-4936-b531-146473fb913c", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这道题考查的是对科技发展与社会关系的辩证思考。我们来分析各个选项：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①</span><span>&zwnj;正确&zwnj;。活动重点推广\"拱手礼、微笑礼\"等传统礼仪，直接传承中华优秀传统文化。能显著提升学生文明素养，</span><span>符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②</span><span>&zwnj;正确&zwnj;。通过校园</span><span>文明礼仪、</span><span>文明用语推广</span><span>的</span><span>形式，</span><span>能够</span><span>有效改善校园人际关系</span><span>，营造和谐友爱的校园氛围，符合题意；</span><span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③</span><span>&zwnj;错误&zwnj;。题干明确活动聚焦\"礼仪教育\"，</span><span>而非</span><span>网络法治教育，活动内容未涉及法治意识培养或网络行为规范</span><span>，不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④</span><span>&zwnj;正确&zwnj;。活动</span><span>由社会组织发起，</span><span>家庭、学校</span><span>积极响应，</span><span>共同参与，</span><span>体现了家校社协同育人，符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>因此，正确答案是B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）2025年，广东省文明办联合省教育厅在全省中小学持续开展\"粤礼粤美\"文明礼仪教育实践活动，重点推广\"拱手礼、微笑礼\"和\"校园文明用语\"。该活动开展一年来，各地学校通过主题班会、亲子情景剧展演等形式深化教育效果。此项活动的积极影响是（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①传承中华传统礼仪文化，提升学生文明素养</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②营造和谐友爱的校园氛围，减少校园冲突</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③增强学生法治意识，规范网络言行</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④推动家校社协同育人机制的完善</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）2025年，广东省文明办联合省教育厅在全省中小学持续开展\"粤礼粤美\"文明礼仪教育实践活动，重点推广\"拱手礼、微笑礼\"和\"校园文明用语\"。该活动开展一年来，各地学校通过主题班会、亲子情景剧展演等形式深化教育效果。此项活动的积极影响是（ ）①传承中华传统礼仪文化，提升学生文明素养②营造和谐友爱的校园氛围，减少校园冲突③增强学生法治意识，规范网络言行④推动家校社协同育人机制的完善", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/739d2fc1-d05b-4936-b531-146473fb913c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984621256", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①②③ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①②④ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: jus